title: The Ride (2013) (digital) (Son of Ultron-Empire)cbr
description:
The flagship title of the 12 Gauge line, The Ride was conceived by company president Keven Gardner to be--both literally and figuratively--a "vehicle" for some of the comics industry's leading lights to create stories around. That "vehicle" is a 1968 Camaro, the unifying element through these stories of bullets, babes, murder, and mayhem! Issue #1 features 2 stories, both of which are illustrated by a different member of Gaijin Studios, each written by 12 Gauge Managing Editor Doug Wagner!
